  "description": "FLO1K provides global, spatially continuous gridded maps of annual streamflow at ~1 km (30 arc-second) resolution for each year from 1960 through 2015. Annual flow metrics include mean annual flow as well as minimum and maximum monthly flow for a given year. The dataset is intended for hydrology, freshwater ecology, water resources assessment, and large-scale environmental modeling applications.",
